==
Rubitron is a simple game defending a stash.  It is made with Rubygame.
==
Installation credit (Kiba):

To install Ruby and rubygems (if you don't already have them):

sudo apt-get install ruby irb ri rubygems ruby-dev

To install rubygame and its SDL dependencies:

sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2-all libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-gfx1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-mixer1.2-dev 
libsdl-ttf2.0-dev

You may also need to install libsdl1.2debian-pulseaudio

sudo gem install rubygame --platform=ruby

